<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Solecism</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-12-03 07:03:32</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>My friend is doing this quest, and I am helping him here and there with it. She is a lvl 20 wizard. When she tried going into Qeynos Aqueducts to find the Shark Pool, she ran right into a spectre, which is a new addition to the sewers since the last patch. It aggros my friend before she can see it, and even repeats this after he is dead so he cant retrieve his own corpse. He is very frustrated with this recent change, and got a no help reply from a petition.<BR>
<BR>
Other than that, I have heard that also with the most recent patch the sharks in Erud's Crossing are just not there. Maybe it is relative to time of day as suggeted earlier, but this is unproven by me. I heard about it at Graffe.com , a wonderful site for wizards.<BR>
-==- Solecism Nolastname<BR>
Brell Serilis server</font></td></tr></table>
