<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>The story of the Sharks is true..I just recently finished the Quest last night and there were no sharks to be seen. Aside from killing those puny undead pirates everything was clear. This was during day time though but cant confirm the day or night spawn of these sharks. I'd say just keep it hush, hush or Verant might go and fix this if it is indeed a bug. </font></td></tr></table>
